channel.title: The Meeting House Video
channel.description: The Meeting House is a church for people who aren't into church. We believe that when you see Jesus without the religious baggage we've historically put around him, you'll find someone undeniably life-changing and worth following. He teaches us to value peace, simplicity, and community. For more information or to visit one of our 18 sites check out: themeetinghouse.com.
